Australia’s women are set to face off against India in their third match of the T20I series. The first two matches ended in a draw with Australia winning both encounters. This sets up an intriguing scenario for the final T20I, where both teams will be looking to secure victory and claim a 3-0 win.

India’s victory in their previous game was particularly significant as it brought them back into contention for a series win. This series has been closely contested, which adds to the tension and anticipation of today's match.
